    "description": "在这款复古的卡牌游戏中，你将是人类最后的防线。对战一波又一波<strong>SPACE INVADERS</strong>，利用手中卡牌赢得胜利！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>踏上加农炮级重型护卫舰的舰桥。智取入侵的部队和敌对指挥官，争夺<strong>HI-SCORE</strong>统治。在这款取材于经典街机游戏的多人战略纸牌游戏中取得更高的排名。<br><br>这副牌是你的，指挥官！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.webp?t=1772028448\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=60 /></picture></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><i>《SPACE INVADERS：Deck Commander》</i>是一款快节奏的战略牌组构建游戏。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>从一副为飞船提供动力的基本卡牌开始逐步发展自己的实力。每个回合中，你都将会发现新的行动卡牌并自定义你的牌组，并制定新的策略。平衡搭配牌组，最大化分数乘数，阻止<strong>INVADERS</strong>。创建属于你自己的强大攻击组合，智取对手指挥官并赢下<strong>HI-SCORE</strong>。成为第一个干掉神秘<strong>UFO</strong>的英雄，阻止入侵。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>与好友在线对战，提升<strong>RANK</strong>，成为排行榜上的新秀。你也可以在离线模式中与机器人练习磨炼技艺。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>- 适合新手和卡牌老手的动态牌组构建游戏。<br>- 在每场比赛中发现强大的新牌组。<br>- 快节奏游戏，体验丰富且快速的玩法。<br>- 在2到4名玩家的在线排位赛中与好友及对手一较高下。<br>- 在全球在线排行榜中证明自己的实力。<br>- 对战难缠的机器人，练习你的指挥和牌组技巧。<br>- 更多秘密即将揭晓......<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>入侵在即！",
